headline: Billie Eilish, Role Model
abstract: The Grammy-winning artist is showing young people a path to being themselves.
lead_paragraph: Mila Docheva faced down the camera, her contours camouflaged by an outsize hoodie raucously inscribed with neon graffiti. Her turnout, which she posted on Instagram, was a homage to her idol, the pop star Billie Eilish.
